10:T43c,High-Oleic Sunflower Oil (HOSO) is a premium edible oil prized for its oxidative stability, neutral flavour, and high monounsaturated fat content — increasingly demanded by food manufacturers seeking clean-label frying and formulation oils. XRT Group sources HOSO from Ukrainian and broader Black Sea producing regions.

**Quality Specification**

High-oleic grade: oleic acid 82% minimum, linoleic acid 10% maximum, FFA 0.1% max, peroxide value 10 max. Bureau Veritas conducts fatty-acid profile and quality certification at load port.

**Logistics**

Bulk liquid tanker and flexi-tank loading from Black Sea ports (subject to corridor availability and insurance). ISO tank and drum packing for smaller parcels. Singapore and Rotterdam hubs provide re-export and blending.

**Pricing**

Differential to Platts Sunflower Oil assessment. Current indicative premium +$20/MT reflecting high-oleic specification premium over standard grade.

**Applications**

Premium frying oil, infant formula and clean-label food manufacturing, cosmetics and personal care, nutraceutical carrier oil.8:["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12 pt-10 sm:pt-16 pb-10 sm:pb-12","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_400px] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"label-caps px-3 py-1.5 border","style":{"color":"#c8973a","borderColor":"#c8973a"},"children":"OIL-004"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"label-caps text-xrt-steel/40","children":"Edible & Industrial Oils"}]]}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-[clamp(2.25rem,6vw,4.5rem)] text-white leading-[1.0] mb-4","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-barlow)","fontWeight":900,"letterSpacing":"-0.02em","textTransform":"uppercase"},"children":"High-Oleic Sunflower Oil"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base text-xrt-steel/50 mb-8","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-archivo)","letterSpacing":"0.04em"},"children":"Oleic 82%+ / Linoleic 10%"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base sm:text-lg text-xrt-steel/70 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-archivo)"},"children":"High-Oleic Sunflower Oil, 82%+ oleic content, from Ukraine and Black Sea origins. Platts SFO benchmark at +$20/MT. Minimum 1,000 MT, FOB/CFR. Bureau Veritas inspection. FOSFA terms."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 border-t border-xrt-steel/15","children":[["$","div","Min. Volume",{"className":"py-5 sm:py-6 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-xrt-steel/15 sm:px-6 sm:first:pl-0","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"label-caps text-xrt-steel/40 mb-2","children":"Min. Volume"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-black text-white","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-barlow)","letterSpacing":"-0.02em"},"children":"1,000 MT"}]]}],["$","div","Benchmark",{"class